summary: AN ORDINANCE vacating a portion of Northeast Pacific Street pursuant to Chapter 35.79 Revised Code of Washington (RCW) and Seattle Municipal Code (SMC) Chapter 15.62, accepting a deed for General Municipal Purposes and assigning jurisdiction to the Engineering Department for Street Purposes, and authorizing the Mayor to sign and the Comptroller to attest to a deed to the Dunn Lumber Co. Inc. (Comptroller File No. 297146; Resolution 27952).
